title: Daniel Preda tells all…
description:
Hello Fools! This week we bring in our very first guest and one of the best people you’ll ever meet… Daniel Preda! We talk cancel culture, finding yourself after being in an internet relationship, how to deal with TAKERS while being a giver, and much more!
Follow Daniel Preda on IG: @misterpreda
Follow Laura on IG: @larlarlee
Follow Manny on IG: @mannymua733
